== Suggested Roles==
The Claymore utilizes its Phantom missiles at relatively long range to destroy [[:Category:Capital Ships|capital ships]] and [[stations]]. It must not go toe-to-toe against any fighter as the Claymore lacks adequate defenses against them. It requires a fighter wing to escort it when performing bombing runs.

